DISCLAIMER AND ATTRIBUTION:

This project was inspired by the original "Motivation" extension created by
Alex MacCaw (https://github.com/maccman/motivation) in 2013. This is an
independent implementation that maintains the core concept while modernizing
the codebase for current web standards and Chrome extension requirements.

The original concept and design inspiration are credited to Alex MacCaw.
This implementation is provided as an independent project to continue
serving users who found value in the original extension.

If you are the original author and have concerns about this project,
please contact [your-email] and we will address them promptly.
